            4 kilobyte demo made for the 4K democompo at Instanssi 2026.
          </p>
          <div class="project-tech">
            <span class="tech-tag">Demo Scene</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">JavaScript</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Shaders</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="project-card">
          <div class="project-header">
            <h3>This website</h3>
            <span class="project-link"><a href="https://github.com/LKKarjalainen/lassikarjalainen" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">View on GitHub</a></span>
          </div>
          <p class="project-description">
            The github repository housing this website project. You can find some easter eggs in the code :)
